    %% External flows
    Client -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS (edge)<br/>Bearer Token"| RegistryRoute
    Client -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS (edge)<br/>Bearer Token"| CatalogRoute

    %% Ingress to auth
    RegistryRoute -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (reencrypt)<br/>NetworkPolicy: ingress ns"| RegistryKRBP
    CatalogRoute -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (reencrypt)<br/>NetworkPolicy: ingress ns"| CatalogKRBP

    %% Auth to K8s API (SubjectAccessReview)
    RegistryKRBP -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>TokenReview +<br/>SubjectAccessReview"| K8sAPI
    CatalogKRBP -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>TokenReview +<br/>SubjectAccessReview"| K8sAPI

    %% Auth to application
    RegistryKRBP -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>plaintext (localhost)<br/>pre-authorized"| RestAPI
    CatalogKRBP -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>plaintext (localhost)<br/>pre-authorized"| CatalogAPI

    %% Application to data
    RestAPI --> GRPC
    RestAPI -->|"PostgreSQL/5432<br/>Configurable SSL<br/>Password"| AutoPG
    RestAPI -->|"PostgreSQL/5432<br/>Configurable SSL"| ExtPG
    RestAPI -->|"MySQL/3306<br/>Optional TLS"| ExtMySQL
    CatalogAPI -->|"PostgreSQL/5432<br/>Password"| CatPG

    %% Operator flows
    OperatorMgr -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>SA token"| K8sAPI
    MetricsKRBP -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS"| K8sAPI
    K8sAPI -->|"HTTPS/9443<br/>mTLS<br/>Webhook calls"| OperatorMgr

